    // REVIEW: Checks if LOC+172 is absent entirely, or if DE3225 (elements[1][0], the Bezeichnung) is empty/missing within the LOC+172 segment. Returns True in either case as the condition is 'DE3225 nicht vorhanden'. (medium confidence)
